🌍 TravelBuddy Map App
TravelBuddy is an interactive map application built with React, Leaflet, and Node.js that allows users to explore locations, leave reviews, and rate places. Authenticated users can drop pins on a map, write descriptions, and rate their experiences.

🚀 Features
📍 View location-based pins with reviews

✨ Authenticated users can add new places (title, description, rating)

🔐 User authentication (Register/Login)

🧭 Automatically centers map on selected marker

📅 Shows when pins were created (e.g., "3 days ago")

🎨 Custom SVG icons for pins

🌍 Leaflet-based interactive OpenStreetMap rendering

🧹 Clean, modular code with React components

